Yes, jupyter notebook shows just this message on the screen. I don't know if it has a different kind of log error output.

I did a little change in the code, specific in that last line. The new line is:

teste = mnist.test.next_batch(1500)
print("test accuracy %g"%accuracy.eval(feed_dict={x:teste[0], y_: teste[1], keep_prob: 1.0}))

And the code ran fine.
I am suspicious that is a memory problem.
What do you think?
